				<div class="hvres-meaning"><a href="/whv/亂"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#xF91B;</span></a><a href="/whv/𥂽"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x250BD;</span></a><a href="/whv/𠏢"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x203E2;</span></a><a href="/whv/薍"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x858D;</span></a><a href="/whv/𤳞"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x24CDE;</span></a><a href="/whv/𢿳"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x22FF3;</span></a><a href="/whv/𢿢"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x22FE2;</span></a><a href="/whv/𡡗"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x21857;</span></a><a href="/whv/辭"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x8FAD;</span></a><a href="/whv/覶"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x89B6;</span></a><p class="gray small" style="padding-left:10px"><a href="/fonts.php">Không hiện chữ?</a></p></div><p class="hvres-source">Một số bài thơ có sử dụng</p>
